INSERT INTO
    fishing_spot_predictions (
    latitude,longitude,species_group_id,week,year
   )
SELECT
    *
FROM
    UNNEST(
        $1::DOUBLE PRECISION[],$2::DOUBLE PRECISION[],$3::INT[],$4::INT[],$5::INT[]
    )
        ON CONFLICT (species_group_id, week, year) DO UPDATE SET latitude = EXCLUDED.latitude,longitude = EXCLUDED.longitude
